snippet.textDisplay:
I love this tribute Dr. Dre.
We are Lower Merion residents who has been blessed to have been of advantage to Kobe’s unconditional kindliness,benevolence, and open-handedness. He held such an authentic character within himself. My family and I are severely disheartened re: he, his princess, and the 7 other’s expiries. One of the things that every human being have in common, is that we all will expire someday. I think that it’s important to be a living soul that can make a positive impact on other people’s lives while we’re still living. It’s also critical that your good will outweigh your bad. Kobe Bryant fulfilled those accomplishments. Kobe also left a lasting impression not only on the people in his circle, but on the world. My family and I will continue to send prayers up for the families that lost their love ones in this catastrophic collision.
